{"tid":1611121,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"AA膠塞鎖匙孔！AA膠塞鎖匙孔！AA膠塞鎖匙孔！","createTime":"2019-10-02T01:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T02:10:49.000Z","uid":108757,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6a16fbaefb403e0c052f9280dd5e30ca3f5a3870","tid":1611121,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:16:00.000Z","msg":"防止狗從地鐵出口衝出嚟。<br />\n出口道閘會有一把鎖頭，一條鐵鏈。最簡單<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">擠AA膠落去，塞鎖匙孔</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESw0eFZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESw0eFZ.png&h=7f610735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n+<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8n3aBUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8n3aBUk.jpg&h=e4c2faf1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推到一人一支，塞佢老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"a24bf6a28ff0f2ec9944c337625bfdbad2b6b789","tid":1611121,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80f332cc3a2b45fc8966b9c25ad27ecf6a96e66","tid":1611121,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:18:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0df3c17a8414af03f5fdbb80396de3a0ddd7be67","tid":1611121,"uid":108757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:19:09.000Z","msg":"人地收數佬都係咁用"},{"pid":"3aab64c8fc61d6ec2f39874c4da80165af4c94cb","tid":1611121,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ed4ba32fee4795f8945ee9e3dc23b8fe9f5e6d","tid":1611121,"uid":116910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"斧頭一下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji